## Config File Schema

Location: `~/.config/<name>/config.yaml` (or `--config` override)

```yaml
# All fields optional; defaults shown
default_format: text       # text | json
verbose: false
[field]: [default]
```

Environment variable overrides: `<TOOLNAME>_CONFIG`, `<TOOLNAME>_VERBOSE`, etc.
